{"tid":1360225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新創建傳考慮出售城巴新巴等資產","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:02:26.000Z","uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d84bc164b4bd2b73df438d04f209c4cf26bcc16e","tid":1360225,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?isapp=1&amp;id=522724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fisapp%3D1%26id%3D522724&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9XIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=07645545\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?isapp=1&amp;id=522724</a><br />\n<br />\n【信報財經新聞】外電引述知情人士透露，新創建集團(00659)考慮出售公共交通資產，涉資約3億美元(約23.4億港元)。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士表示，新創建出售的資產包括城巴、新巴等。該公司正與潛在買家包括招商局集團等磋商。<br />\n<br />\n城巴及新巴目前合共有超過1600部巴士，經營約200條路線。2018年巴士業務盈利下跌63%至1.27億元。另外，新創建還營運離島及港內航線之渡輪業務。<br />\n<br />\n愛國愛港巴士團隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}